targets.rawSql:
select * from ip_duplication inner join (
select ip_address from ip_duplication group by ip_address having count(ip_address) > 1
) dup on  dup.ip_address = ip_duplication.ip_address and dup.ip_address != "None"
where ip_duplication.instance_name = $instance_name
order by ip_duplication.ip_address
